Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:02:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of the home of the director of Kiyama Furniture, the best in the industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the garden is outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've seen a garden with a waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's somewhat calming, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's starting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something for you to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The basin under the waterfall is overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water is pooling in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were surprised, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That happens thrice a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning and evenings at 8:00 and at 4:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water from the fall will overflow into the structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, don't the patterns of the sand disappear when that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water fills in slowly without disrupting it, and drains away after thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was a device created by the previous director, and this is quite popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, pardon me while I attend to some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do relax until the dinner party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And please do not worry about the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will have a mechanic look at it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry for troubling you over everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're all the same when troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Ayaka, I'll leave everyone in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood, director.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's quite a magnificent thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a superficial thing that costs a lot in maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief, that Kiyama sure made an outrageous garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wave patterns on the white sand looks so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:03:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it'd be gorgeous when the moonlight reflects upon it at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, extremely so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Among the frequent clients, there are some who visit during the full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Savoring cold sake and basking in the full moon in view of the Fuji mountains, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Simply irresistible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that, Onee{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's leaning against that pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the picking rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Picking rod?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When anything falls on the white sands in the gardens...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We extend it like this to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't possibly step on the precious wave patterns of the white sands, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's well thought out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since Director Majima took over, the gardener only comes by once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's starting to drain out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's sure well made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you please, shall we head out to the Salon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will prepare some aperitifs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just what I've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, they said it was an inferior surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiots, speaking without thinking carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just five million more, no, including interest, it's seven million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Return all of it by the middle of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This western style house is impressive too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, please enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that man from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will bring some refreshments immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If possible, I'd like a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only noon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are guests of Director Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, no, we're nothing of such importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, our car ran out of gas on the mountain roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Director Majima, who happened to be passing by, called out to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he kindly invited us for dinner as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, that's really a fine and sociable director.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, showing only his fine side to outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight's the annual dinner where we review Kiyama's financial statements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the involved parties should be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter, right Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did invite them after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, it's enjoyable to have more people during meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the Director of our group's branch company, Kiyama Interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the past, Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was accomplished in archery on a national level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.12,0:08:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you possibly be that same Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from Africa Style Travels?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know him, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he travels to different countries and writes books about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I read Africa Style Travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was deeply moved by it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, may I get your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm having a photography exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do drop by if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just sign for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty old fountain pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a memento from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing much, but I couldn't let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I always have it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do invite your friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll definitely enjoy it with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never knew that Tomonori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was part of the Kiyama Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a company that my father built in his lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After father died, Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, have you seen the rock garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the patterns on the white sands were truly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That white sand and waterfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father made them with laborious determination on his breaks during busy periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how did Tomonori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s father pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, that's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a traffic accident last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A person's destiny is indeed unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there's a spot with a great night view nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we go see it later?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go and see it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were to choose, I'd rather be drinking sake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be better to go though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's worth having a glimpse at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike Tokyo, the stars really draw close here, and it feels like you can touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stars, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's here, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for these!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides beers, you could try the other drinks if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have more on-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I shall try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, stop that or it'll spill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of the alcohol already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, he sure has a soft spot for alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, have another glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to impose on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:11:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've been in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'll be having a photo exhibition soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be great if you would come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Photo exhibition, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Tomonari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} seems to be working really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Director, this is last month's sales report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope that the figures at least would be decently average, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Director, dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's head to the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dinner party, dinner party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, here's wishing for the continuous growth of Kiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This meat is delicious, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's really tender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, please have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for imposing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really like it that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This must be some twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall allow it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you can take your time discussing it with your father before deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I should take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I shall excuse myself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a video I'd like to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could we go night viewing after that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I'll come and get you around 11:15 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what video that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to watch an adventure or a documentary on Sekiguchi Hiroiken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to find them and brought it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph, an adventure or documentary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because he's engrossed in these things that Majima has taken over the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hashimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is not that sort of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, what's the matter, Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How unusual for you to be on Majima's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's useless to do that at this point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you being scapegoated for the poor business performance and getting fired next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the deficit in Kiyama Interior was caused by the deficit of the main company, Kiyama Furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were just used to spread the threat around that's all, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I get fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone is worried though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that rate, you might even murder Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it there, Hashimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really making me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I shall take my leave too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still have work at the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, about that matter earlier, you'd better not go ahead with it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That matter earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you were discussing at the table earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll show a nice front to drag you in, and once you're close, you'll never get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is the way Majima does things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's better not to get too involved with a guy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hashimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, let's head back soon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just a little more wouldn't hurt, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows what will come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we're drinking, we should just drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you do say some nice things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's this late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, should we get back to our rooms soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get back to the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's still a bottle of beer left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When drinking, we should just drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry about the fuss we're causing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can still drink though...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Medication for a hangover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be here if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just call for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on walk straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did something terrible to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have forced himself to accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't mind it, this is quite common.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're coming
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the video interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a really intense documentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we'll be going night viewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Mouri should have come along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of when I was a child, coming here with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father loved this night view too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was the night scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was extremely beautiful—I'm so touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's voice was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:20:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Director Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that scream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, call the police immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To maintain the crime scene, please do not enter the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acting so arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mouri Kogorou, a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Mouri Kogorou"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but don't you find the director's body strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's strange about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are no foot prints around his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how did Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} end up there?
